v^3/u^2=k
k
u,v \gt 0
v^2 \, du^2-2uv \, du+2u^2 \, dv^2
(r^{'},r^{''},n)=0
r(u,v)=v^{3}-ku^{2}=0
(r^{'},r^{''},n)=(r^{'}\times{r^{''}})\cdot{n}=\vert{r^{'}}\vert\cdot\vert{r^{''}}\vert\sin\theta{\cdot{n}}
sin\theta=0$$\Longrightarrow{cos\theta}=1$$\Longrightarrow$$\frac{r^{'}\cdot{r^{''}}}{\vert{r^{'}}\vert\vert{r^{''}}\vert}=1
\Longrightarrow{cos\theta}=1
r^{'}=(-2ku,3v^{2})
r^{''}=(-2k,6v)
